weather\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fyoutube.com%2FHKGweather&d=JC%2BoF4fRaZyKvWcl7nla%2FMv4r%2BPR%2BKiJG6VnsQYGapQ%3D&h=306681a9\" target=\"_blank\">http://youtube.com/HKGweather</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: purple;\"><ins>◤溫度術語</ins></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: navy;\">嚴寒 　　　　　≦ 7 &deg;C</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">寒冷 　 　　　8 - 12 &deg;C</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\">清涼　　　　13 - 17 &deg;C</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">和暖／稍涼　18 - 22 &deg;C</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">溫暖　　　　23 - 27 &deg;C</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">炎熱　　　　28 - 32 &deg;C</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: maroon;\">酷熱 　　 　　≧ 33 &deg;C</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: navy;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><ins>◤參考網頁</ins></span></span><br />\n◆ 實時天氣照片：<a href=\"http://www.hko.gov.hk/wxinfo/ts/index_webcam_uc.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hko.gov.hk%2Fwxinfo%2Fts%2Findex_webcam_uc.htm&d=JC%2BoF4fRaZyKvWcl7nla%2FMv4r%2BPR%2BKiJG6VnsQYGapQ%3D&h=49954a67\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hko.gov.hk/wxinfo/ts/index_webcam_uc.htm</a><br />\n◆ 天氣雷達圖像：<a href=\"http://www.hko.gov.hk/wxinfo/radars/radarc_range1.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hko.gov.hk%2Fwxinfo%2Fradars%2Fradarc_range1.htm&d=JC%2BoF4fRaZyKvWcl7nla%2FMv4r%2BPR%2BKiJG6VnsQYGapQ%3D&h=243bbf20\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hko.gov.hk/wxinfo/radars/radarc_range1.htm</a><br />\n◆ 機場天氣預報：<a href=\"http://www.hko.gov.hk/aviat/taf_decode.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hko.gov.hk%2Faviat%2Ftaf_decode.htm&d=JC%2BoF4fRaZyKvWcl7nla%2FMv4r%2BPR%2BKiJG6VnsQYGapQ%3D&h=1a165fd7\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hko.gov.hk/aviat/taf_decode.htm</a><br />\n◆ 認識天氣現象：<a href=